      "date": "2012-01-27 02:01:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/f5f6602a-4876-11e1-b292-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 17 tests.  1 tests failed: conf-sanity.",
