        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2012-01-28 00:41:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAdded Ihara, since he is the original developer of the LU-241 patch, and is most likely to be the person using this code in production.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
